University of Bristol study found drinking 'one large glass of wine' increases 'facial flushing' and 'confidence' But too much booze leads to 'excessive and unattractive' facial expressions . 
  Study found alcohol has 'positive pulling power' but only if the person isn't drunk . 
  40 heterosexual men and women were asked to rate three groups of people - sober, tipsy and drunk . 
  Tipsy people consistently voted 'most attractive'